<section id="decision-rule" class="px-6 py-10 md:py-14">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl">
    <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[1.05fr_0.95fr] lg:items-start lg:gap-12">
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-argmin-dark">Why Argmin</p>
        <h2 class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-3xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.04em] text-argmin-dark md:text-5xl">
          Every inference request is a decision problem.
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-5 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-argmin-dark md:text-xl">
          Argmin asks a simple question at request time: which action minimizes total risk-adjusted cost?
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 rounded-[2rem] border border-argmin-border bg-white/80 p-6 shadow-[0_24px_60px_rgba(15,23,42,0.08)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
