          <div class="equation-wrap mt-6 overflow-x-auto">
            <div class="equation min-w-[320px] text-argmin-dark">
              <div class="equation-operator">arg&nbsp;min</div>
              <div class="equation-subscript">a ∈ Actions</div>
              <div class="equation-expression">TRAC(a)</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-base leading-relaxed text-argmin-dark">
            The decision engine retrieves attribution data and conditionally permits, modifies, or redirects
            the request based on the lowest-risk, lowest-cost available action.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-4">
        <article class="rounded-[1.75rem] border border-argmin-border bg-argmin-surface/80 p-6 shadow-[0_24px_60px_rgba(15,23,42,0.08)] backdrop-blur">
