          <p class="mt-3 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.03em] text-argmin-dark">The available moves.</p>
          <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-argmin-dark">
            Model choice, routing decision, region, and configuration. Argmin evaluates the viable options
            before the request goes through.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="rounded-[1.75rem] border border-argmin-border bg-argmin-surface/80 p-6 shadow-[0_24px_60px_rgba(15,23,42,0.08)] backdrop-blur">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-argmin-dark">TRAC</p>
          <p class="mt-3 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.03em] text-argmin-dark">Total Risk-Adjusted Cost.</p>
          <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-argmin-dark">
            Direct cost plus a confidence risk premium. Not just what the request costs, but how risky that
            choice is for the business.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="rounded-[1.75rem] border border-argmin-border bg-gradient-to-br from-argmin-accent/18 via-white/90 to-white/65 p-6 shadow-[0_24px_60px_rgba(15,23,42,0.08)] backdrop-blur">
